race.description: Isla Vodka Happy 21St Paddy Mdn Plate
race.comment: POETS ARTISTRY (3) is a three-year-old gelding by Trapeze Artist on debut for the Hayes yard. Was in the placings in his most recent trial at Pakenham and must respect the top yard here. OFFA'S DYKE (2) stepped out for his debut over 1000m at Mildura back on July 19 and finished fifth, beaten 6 lengths. Was in the market there and could be a quick improver. CINNAMON KISS (8) debuts. Has shown enough in the trials to suspect she can be a factor in a race which lacks much in terms of depth after some key scratchings. BRAVE CHARM (6) hasn't shown much on raceday to date however trials in readiness for this campaign have indicated ability.
